flowchart LR
  Controller[Controller] --> Service[Service]
  Service --> Domain[Domain helpers and invariants]
  Service --> Repository[Repository]
  Repository --> Selects[Explicit select lists]
  Repository --> Filters[User-scoped where filters]
  Repository --> Pagination[Shared cursor helpers]
  Repository --> Aggregates[aggregate groupBy raw SQL]
  Repository --> Prisma[Prisma client or transaction client]
  Prisma --> Database[(PostgreSQL)]

  Service -. owns .-> Orchestration[Flow transaction scope errors mapper calls]
  Repository -. owns .-> QueryShape[Indexes joins filters sorting performance]
  Domain -. owns .-> Rules[Reusable pure business rules]
